    Contains concrete descendants of the abstract tester classes defined in TesterClasses. These concrete classes are intended to test specific Quadruple operations, e.g. Quadruple.toString() is tested by an instance of SpecificTesterClasses.QuadToStringTester. The general logic of these classes is described in more detail in the descriptions of their respective ancestors such as TesterClasses.Conversion_Q2T_Tester, TesterClasses.Conversion_T2Q_Tester and others, nested in TesterClasses.
